title: Alex Jones Thursday 3-19-09 - www.AlexJonesPodcasts.com
description:
From www.AlexJonesPodcasts.com - Alex Jones Show archive:

Thursday March 19, 2009

Alex welcomes to the show Chuck Baldwin, the founder-pastor of Crossroad Baptist Church in Pensacola, Florida, and presidential nominee of the Constitution Party for the 2008 U.S. Presidential election. Alex also talks with Commander David K. Rehbein of The American Legion, who is opposed to Obama's proposal to force private insurance companies to pay for the treatment of military veterans who have suffered service-connected disabilities and injuries. Additional guests include Stewart Rhodes, founder of Oath Keepers, and Jeffrey Grupp, the author of Corporatism: The Secret Government of the New World Order.
